: maximising the potential of green business </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">(2012). CBI. July 2012. Available at: </span><a href="http://www.cbi.org.uk/media/1552876/energy_climatechangerpt_web.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.cbi.org.uk/media/1552876/energy_climatechangerpt_web.pdf</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">. On future economic benefits of low-carbon investment, see: </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">Infographic: how the UK can make the most of green growth</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">. Available at: </span><a href="http://www.cbi.org.uk/infographics/how-the-uk-can-make-the-most-of-green-growth/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.cbi.org.uk/infographics/how-the-uk-can-make-the-most-of-green-growth/</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn10"></a><a href="#_ftnref10">[10]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">One million climate jobs</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> (2010). London. Campaign against Climate Change. October 2010. Available at: </span><a href="http://www.climate-change-jobs.org/sites/default/files/1MillionClimateJobs_2010.PDF"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.climate-change-jobs.org/sites/default/files/1MillionClimateJobs_2010.PDF</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn11"></a><a href="#_ftnref11">[11]</a><span style="font-family